text: Typhoon Noru, known in the Philippines as Super Typhoon Karding, was a tropical cyclone in the Pacific Ocean. The typhoon battered the Philippines and Vietnam in September 2022. Noru struck the Philippines, leaving 5 people dead in San Miguel, Bulacan. ==References== Category:2022 in Asia Noru Noru Category:Typhoons in the Philippines Noru Noru
